Sainsbury's na shirin shiga kasuwar Burtaniya
Sainsbury's zai yi gasa da Boots, SuperDrag da kuma DeBenhams a cikin shaguna masu kama da kantin sayar da kayayyaki da kayan shafawa da kuma ma'aikatan tallafi.
A wani bangare na kokarin da ake yi na shiga kasuwar kayan kwalliyar Burtaniya mai daraja fam biliyan 2.8, za a fara amfani da manyan kayan kwalliyar a shaguna 11 a fadin kasar, idan aka samu nasara za a fara amfani da su a wasu shaguna.
Wannan saka hannun jari yana zuwa ne yayin da manyan kantunan ke neman sabbin hanyoyin cike ɗakunan ajiya da suka taɓa cika da TVs, microwaves da kayan ado na gida.
