Wani yunkuri da aka yi a baya na sake fasalin babban kanti da kuma sashen kantin magani ya gaza.
Sainsbury's ta gwada wani haɗin gwiwa tare da Fike Boots a farkon 2000s amma an dakatar da aikin saboda rikice-rikice game da yadda za a raba ribar da aka samu daga kantin likitancin a cikin manyan kantuna.
