A lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya kaddamar da wani taron yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne farkon taron rukuni biyar da aka tsara na Trump a mako mai zuwa, tare da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da kuri'un tabbatar da zabensa don cike gurbin kotun koli ke cikin tsaka-tsaki, Trump na kan hanyar gina goyon baya don zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa ikon majalisar dokoki bayan zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump na yammacin Virginia a daren yau kuma ta yaya kuke kallon sa ta yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na dare, wannan daren Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump na West Virginia a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai yi jawabi a wannan makon game da sauraron wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi tashin hankali saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i a yayin binciken FBI tare da kuri'ar tabbatar da majalisar dattijai.
Amma babban burin da aka fara gudanar da taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican samun ci gaba a gaban zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wannan hanyar, kamfen din Shugaba Trump ya ce gangamin gangamin biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa na nufin "karfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar sa, don haka shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda ya yiwu yayin da muke shiga cikin lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump wanda bai so a bayyana sunansa ba.
An shirya taron ne a Wesenbenko Arena a Wheeling, taron na yau zai iya "kawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma samun rahoto daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
Wannan shine karo na biyu da Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia tun watan da ya gabata, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
A yayin da ake neman zaben, Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya ragu a zaben.
A cewar Reuters, Simon Heather, wani dan siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, ya ce "ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Mr. Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya yi kokarin kara karfafa shi a zaben".
Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA ta nuna yunwar ta ci gaba da fafatawa a gasar cin kofin Ryder Cup a ranar Lahadi
A ranar Asabar da yamma ne ake bukatar gasar Ryder Cup bayan an yi zaman uku.
Motsawar motsi na motsi shine cikakkiyar ra'ayin wasanni amma 'yan wasa sun gaskanta da gaske, kuma mafi yawa a irin wannan gasar.
To, ina za su ce Momentum yanzu?
"Suna da ci gaba da maki shida kuma yanzu sun kai hudu, don haka ina tsammanin muna da ɗan lokaci yanzu", Jordan Speith ya ce don tafiya a ranar.
Turai tana da fa'ida, tabbas, tana da maki hudu da sauran wasanni 12.
Kamar yadda Speith ya ce, Amurkawa suna jin cewa suna da wasu taimako a kan hanya kuma suna iya samun ƙarfafawa daga abubuwa da yawa, musamman yanayin Speeth da Justin Thomas waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma dukansu sun sami maki huɗu zuwa uku.
Speeth ya kasance mai kisa daga farko zuwa ƙarshe kuma yana jagorantar gaba.
Ya yi ihu da murya mai ƙarfi yayin da yake zagaye, yana yin babbar rawa don cin nasarar wasan da aka yi na maki huɗu, yayin da shi da Thomas suka ci biyu duk da cewa sun ci biyu.
A ranar 15 ga watan Agusta, ya yi ihu kamar yadda ya yi a wasan da ya lashe, wanda hakan ya nuna cewa ya yi imanin cewa 'yan wasan Amurka ba su da matsala.
"Dole ne ku zurfafa sosai kuma ku yi tunani game da wasanku", in ji Speith.
Kowane daga cikin 'yan wasan yanzu yana da wannan.
Ramin 18 don yin alama.
'Yan wasan da suka samu maki fiye da Speith da Thomas a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francisco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, labarin rashin adalci na Ryder Cup.
Ƙari ga haka, wasu ma'aurata a Turai suna da kyau sosai.
"Mollywood" ita ce kawai ma'aurata da ba su yi harbi a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, amma sun guje wa motar a ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da yamma, da kuma tara na yamma a ranar Jumma'a.
Wannan tseren, da kuma yadda ƙarfin su ya gudana zuwa da daga wannan taron masu farin ciki, ya nuna cewa su ne 'yan wasan da suka rasa ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani ɗan wasa mai yiwuwa da ya fi dacewa da yaƙin Turai fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari yayin da rana ta faɗi a Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau idan duka biyu suna cikin ramuka daban-daban a lokaci guda.
Duk da haka, ba a daɗe da yin magana game da darajar Turai ba.
Buba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi wasu matsaloli ga jarumi Sergio Garcia na wasan kwallon kafa na safe yayin da suke tare da Alex Naren.
A cikin tara na farko, wani bogey da biyu biyu sun jefa Spaniards da Swede a cikin rami wanda ba za su iya tashi ba.
A ranar Lahadi, duk da haka, babu wanda zai fitar da ku daga raminku.
Yana da ban sha'awa sosai a lura da hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, abin da suke ba da shawara, abin da ba su ba da shawara ba, da kuma dabarun da za su iya canzawa nan take.
Turai ta yi wasa da kyau a matsayin kungiya har yanzu kuma ta sami gagarumar nasara a ranar karshe amma wannan zaman na hudu ya kara tabbatar da cewa Team USA na da yunwar yin gwagwarmaya da wasu, musamman ma na jihohi, suka yi shakkar su.
A ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder, Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10 da 6.
Turai za ta ci gajiyar ci gabanta na 10-6 da Amurka ta yi a wasannin Foreball da Foursom a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup.
Ma'aurata masu farin ciki Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun ci gaba da cin nasara sau biyu a kan Tiger Woods biyu da ke shan wahala yanzu suna da maki huɗu a Golf National.
Kungiyar Turai ta Thomas Jorn, wacce ke neman dawo da kofin da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta doke Amurkawa da suka gaza a wasan safe, ta lashe jerin 3-1.
Amurka ta lashe wasanni biyu kuma ta ba da ƙarin juriya a Forums, amma ba su cika rashi ba.
Jim Furyk yana bukatar maki takwas daga wasanni 12 da ya buga a ranar Lahadi don dawo da kofin.
Fleetwood ita ce rookie ta farko a Turai da ta ci kwallaye hudu a jere, kuma ita da Molinari, tare da Malliwood, sune biyu kawai da suka ci kwallaye hudu daga wasannin farko hudu a tarihin Ryder Cup bayan wata babbar karshen mako.
Woods da Patrick Reed sun murƙushe a cikin ƙwallon ƙafa, sannan suka yi nasara da kyau don doke Woods da rookie na Amurka Bryson DeCambeau da ƙarfi ta hanyar 5 da 4.
Woods, wanda ya yi wasa biyu a ranar Asabar, ya yi ta yin gwagwarmaya a wasu lokutan amma yanzu ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 da ya buga a wasan kwallon kafa da kuma wasanni bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, yana hutawa don wasan kwallon kafa na safe, ya koma hannun abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a wasan da ya doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepker 2 da 1 - lamba daya da uku a duniya.
A yammacin kudu maso yammacin Paris a rana mai kyau, iska mai iska, ko da yake Turai ba ta da kanta.
Jordan Speith da Justin Thomas, manyan masu nasara sau uku, sun kafa ma'auni ga Amurkawa da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara mai ƙarfi 2 da 1 akan John Ram da Ian Polter na Spain a cikin Foursquare kuma sun dawo bayan sun doke Polter da Rory McIlroy a 4 da 3 bayan sun sha kashi a ramuka biyu na farko a Foursquare.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da wata kungiya ta dawo daga ragin maki hudu a wasan da ta yi a karo na daya, kodayake a yanzu haka Fury yana bukatar wasa daya ne kawai don dawo da kofin.
Bayan sun kasance na biyu mafi kyau na kwana biyu, duk da haka, bugun bugun ranar Lahadi yana da alama zai wuce su.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta yi watsi da makamai ba tare da amincewa ba.
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa takunkumin da ake da shi na kara zurfafa rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma a irin wannan yanayi ba shi da wata dama da kasar za ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliyarta baki daya.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron shekara-shekara na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "manyan matakai na alheri" a bara, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da na missile, rushe dakin gwaje-gwajen nukiliya, da kuma yin alkawarin hana yaduwar fasahar nukiliya da makaman nukiliya.
"Amma ba mu ga irin wannan martani a Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Idan ba mu da tabbaci a Amurka, ba za mu da tabbaci a tsaron kasa ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayi, ba mu da wata hanyar da za mu iya yin watsi da makamai".
Ko da yake Ri ya bayyana zargin da Koriya ta Arewa ke yi wa Washington na "daidaita" tsarin nukiliya, cewa za a saka wa Koriya ta Arewa da yin aiki a hankali, maganganun nasa sun zama masu mahimmanci saboda bai yi watsi da niyyar yin amfani da makaman nukiliya ba, kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya ambaci wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka fitar a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan "rashin nukiliya na yankin Koriya ta Kudu" kuma lokacin da Trump ya ba da tabbacin tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na neman kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara watsi da makaman nukiliyarta.
Washington ta kuma yi tsayayya da kiran da ake yi na sassauta tsauraran takunkumin kasa da kasa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan 'Yanci da Makamai-Da farko' kuma ta kara matsin lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinta, har ma da" yin adawa da sanarwar kawo karshen yakin", in ji Ri.
"Tunanin cewa takunkumi zai iya lalata mu shine mafarkin waɗanda basu san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, takunkumin da ake ci gaba da yi yana kara tsananta mana rashin amincewa. "
Ri bai yi sharhi kan shirin taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba, wanda shugaban Amurka ya gabatar a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon.
Maimakon haka, Ministan ya yi nuni da ganawa uku da Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in suka yi a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata. "Da ba don Amurka ba, da batun kwantar da hankali ya kasance a Koriya ta Kudu, da kwararar makamai a yankin Koriya ba ta tsaya cik ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya bambanta sosai da na bara, lokacin da ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba za a iya kaucewa kai hari kan Amurka tare da rokokin Koriya ta Arewa ba, yayin da "Mista Shugaba Mugun" Trump ya kira Kim "Mutumin Rokoki".
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya a bara, ya yaba wa Kim saboda karfin gwiwar da ya nuna wajen daukar matakan kwantar da hankali, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma takunkumin zai ci gaba har sai an kwantar da hankalin Koriya ta Arewa.
A ranar Laraba Trump ya ce babu wani lokaci da za a dauka, ya ce, "Idan ya dauki shekaru biyu, ko uku ko watanni biyar kafin a yi shi - ba kome".
China da Rasha sun yi jayayya cewa ya kamata a ba Pyongyang lada saboda matakin da Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya dauka
Duk da haka, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya gaya wa Amurkawa a Majalisar Tsaro a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Hukumar Majalisar Tsaro ta ci gaba da kasancewa mai tasiri har sai mun cimma cikakken tabbatar da tabbatar da makaman".
Majalisar Tsaro ta kara wa Koriya ta Arewa takunkumi tun 2006 bisa amincewar ta, saboda dakatar da bayar da kudade ga shirin nukiliyar Pyongyang da na makamansa.
Pompeo ya gana da Rio a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma ziyarar da ya yi ta ƙarshe ba ta tafi daidai ba.
Ya ce lokacin da ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli, an samu ci gaba, sai da Koriya ta Arewa ta yi masa kashedi da cewa "yana da'awar cewa shi ɗan fashi ne".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rushe wani wurin da ake amfani da makamai masu linzami da kuma wani makaman nukiliya a wani taron da ta yi da Moon a wannan watan idan Amurka ta "yi irin wannan matakin".
Ya ce "matakan da suka dace" da Kim ya gaya masa yana neman su ne na tabbatar da tsaro da Trump ya ba da a Singapore kuma ya ci gaba da daidaita dangantaka da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna karatun samun isasshen hutu.
A wannan shekara, wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard yana ba da shawara ga duk ɗaliban da suka kammala karatunsu su sami ƙarin bacci don magance al'adun masu tsakar dare masu shan maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin ilimi ya gano cewa daliban jami'o'i mafi girma a duniya galibi suna rikicewa game da ainihin abubuwan da suka shafi yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles Siziller, farfesa a likitancin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women's Hospital, ya kirkiro wannan kwas din, wanda ya yi imanin shine na farko a Amurka.
Ta samu kwarin gwiwar fara karatun ne bayan ta ba da jawabi kan yadda rashin bacci ke shafar ilimi.
A ƙarshen, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, "Me ya sa aka gaya mini wannan tun ina ƙaramin shekara?"
Ya ce, "Babu wanda ya taba gaya mata muhimmancin barci - abin da ya ba ni mamaki", in ji shi.
Wannan kwas din, wanda aka fara gudanarwa a wannan shekarar, ya bayyana wa dalibai yadda kyawawan halaye na bacci ke taimakawa a cikin aikin ilimi da wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyarsu.
Paul Barrera, Farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma darektan zartarwa na sashen kiwon lafiya na jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar fara karatun ne bayan da dalibai suka kamu da matsalar rashin bacci a wannan makon.
Wannan darasi na awa daya yana dauke da ayyuka masu nasaba da juna.
Wani sashe yana da hotunan ɗakin kwanan dalibai, inda ɗalibai za su danna kan kofi, allon, masu koyarwa da littattafai don koyi game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki da kuma fahimtar muhimmancin tsarin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an gaya wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya kara hadarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, bakin ciki da ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar makarantar tare da gumakan ma'amala, sannan yana ƙarfafa mahalarta suyi tunani game da al'adarsu ta yau da kullun.
