HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta samu karuwar sabbin masu cutar da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar mutane da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Akwai mutane sama da 820,000 da ke fama da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai, an samu sabbin mutane kusan 40,000.
Yawancin sabbin cututtukan sun kasance ne saboda kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya canza daga abubuwan da suka gabata.
A al'adance, kamuwa da cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar jini.
Amma a wannan hanyar, an rage yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV zuwa kusan sifili, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun fada a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke fama da cutar kanjamau da kanjamau a kasar Sin na karuwa da 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT a kasar Sin.
An halatta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma har yanzu ana nuna nuna wariya ga mutanen LGBT.
Saboda dabi'un kasar masu ra'ayin mazan jiya, binciken ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin dari na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza suna auren mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna zuwa ne daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin wannan dangantaka.
Tun daga 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
