Mene ne bikin 'yan kasa na duniya kuma shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar ne za a yi bikin Global Citizen Festival a New York, wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke da kyakkyawan jerin wasan kwaikwayon taurari da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa; kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, bikin na Global Citizen zai ga dubban mutane suna zagayawa kan babban lawns a Central Park don jin daɗin ayyukan Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba wai kawai don haka ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawo ƙarshen talauci ta 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen wanda aka bayyana a shekarar 2012 wani ci gaba ne na aikin talauci na duniya, wata kungiya da ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fafutukar yaki a duniya.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan ba ku son biyan kuɗin tikitin VIP), masu halartar taron dole ne suyi ayyuka da yawa ko "ayyukan" kamar aikin sa kai, imel ɗin jagorar duniya, kiran waya, ko wasu hanyoyin da za su taimaka wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burinsu na kawo ƙarshen talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar da Global Citizen ke samu a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage don cimma burin?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane ta hanyar ba da kyauta kyauta ne ainihin matakin da za a ɗauka don sa mutane su yi kira zuwa aiki, ko kuma wani yanayin da ake kira "clictivism" - inda mutane ke jin cewa suna yin canji na gaske ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda kan layi ko aika tweet?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ya ce ya rubuta sama da "aiki" miliyan 19 daga magoya bayansa, yana ci gaba da cimma manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce wadannan matakai sun taimaka wa shugabannin duniya su bayyana alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.2 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta yi nuni da alkawura da sanarwa 390 da suka fara aiki, wanda a kalla dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka rarraba ko aka tara.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka samu sun shafi mutane miliyan 649 a duniya har zuwa yanzu.
