"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin kasa da 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya juya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki zuwa tarihin tarihi", in ji Tracy Ullman, jakadan The Power of Nutrition, ga masu sauraro a lokacin wani taron mawaƙa a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an ɗauki matakai sama da 5,000 a Amurka don inganta abinci mai gina jiki na uwa da jariri, gwamnati ta sanar da bayar da kuɗi don wani shiri, The Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 a cikin aikin abinci mai gina jiki.
Tambaya daya da ake yawan yi a shafin yanar gizon ta ita ce "Me kuke ganin za mu iya yi don kawo karshen talauci?"
