Amma, kamar yadda yake a cikin manyan 'yancin jama'a da kuma adawa da wariyar launin fata, za mu yi nasara, domin muna da karfi tare.
Janet Jackson, The Weekend, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Moni suna cikin waɗanda za su yi wasa a bikin wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborah-Lee Farnes da Hugh Jackman za su gudanar.
Amurka na iya amfani da sojan ruwanta don "hana" fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida
Washington na iya amfani da sojojinta "idan ya cancanta" don hana masu amfani da man fetur na Rasha shiga kasashen Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, a cewar mai binciken Washington.
Gink ya yi zargin cewa shigar da Rasha cikin Syria - musamman ma, inda take aiki a gayyatar gwamnati mai halal - uzuri ne don bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Na yi imanin cewa dalilin da ya sa suke a Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne don suna son su yi amfani da wutar lantarki kamar Gabashin Turai, cibiyar kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma a cewar jami'an akwai hanyoyin da za a bi don magance hakan.
Ya ce, "Amurka tana da karfin da ke cikin sojojin ruwanmu na hana su shiga teku, kuma idan ya cancanta, su toshe hanyoyin da za su tabbatar da cewa makamashi ba zai shiga kasuwa ba".
Zinkke yana jawabi ne ga mahalarta taron da kungiyar Consumers Energy Alliance, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke bayyana kanta a matsayin "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke bi da Rasha da Iran, yana mai cewa su daya ne a zahiri.
"Hanyoyin tattalin arziki na Iran da Rasha sun shafi samun fa'ida da maye gurbin makamashi da yawa", in ji shi, "da kuma "ƙaddamar da Rasha tare da tattalin arzikin mai mai", in ji shi.
Wannan magana ta zo ne a daidai lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ke neman karfafa kayayyakin da ake fitarwa na LNG a Turai a kan farashi mai sauki ga masu amfani da shi maimakon Rasha.
