Elizabeth Warren za ta "yi nasara" a neman takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020, in ji Sanatan Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren daga Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta "duba" takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben.
