Sarah Palin ta ambaci PTSD na Track Palin a taron Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki bayan da ya shiga aikin soja a watan Satumba.
An kama shi a daren Litinin kuma an tuhume shi da aikata wani abu na tashin hankali a gida.
