Jihohi 18, DC sun goyi bayan kalubalen sabuwar manufar mafaka
Jihohi 18 da gundumar Columbia suna goyon bayan kalubalen shari'a kan sabuwar manufar Amurka da ke hana ba da mafaka ga wadanda ke tserewa daga kungiyoyi ko tashin hankali na cikin gida.
A cikin goyon bayan wani mai neman mafaka da ya kalubalanci manufar, wakilan jihohi da gundumomi 18 sun gabatar da wata takarda ta abokantaka a kotu a Washington a ranar Juma'a, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace v. Sessions ba, wanda kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta a kan manufofin tarayya.
Ya ce abokan aikinsa "da 'yan kungiyar sa masu ta'addanci" sun yi masa zagon kasa, amma jami'an Amurka sun yi watsi da bukatarsa ta neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
An tsare shi a Texas.
Lauyoyin jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun ba da misalin El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, ƙasashe da ke fama da matsalar ƙungiyoyi da tashin hankali na cikin gida, inda yawancin masu neman mafaka ke zuwa Amurka.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta sauya hukuncin da Hukumar Kula da Shige da Fice ta yanke a shekarar 2014 na barin bakin haure da ba a yi rajista ba da suka tsere daga tashin hankali na cikin gida su nemi mafaka.
Babban lauyan yankin Columbia, Carl Racine, ya fada a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar dokar "ta yi watsi da shekaru da dama na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa".
"Dangane da wannan dokar tarayya, duk bukatar da ake yi wa 'yan gudun hijira ya kamata a yi hukunci a kan wasu bayanai da yanayi, kuma irin wannan haramcin ya sabawa ainihin manufar", in ji takardar.
A cikin sanarwar, lauyoyin sun kara da cewa, manufar hana masu shiga shiga kasar na cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, saboda sun fi dacewa su zama 'yan kasuwa kuma suna "bada aikin yi da ake bukata".
Babban lauyan Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan shige da fice da su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke fama da tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma gungun mutane a watan Yuni.
"Waɗanda suka tilasta barin ƙasarsu saboda tsananin zalunci ko tsoron yin hakan saboda ƙabila, addini, ƙasa ko membobin wata ƙungiyar zamantakewa ko ra'ayoyin siyasa", in ji Sessions a cikin sanarwar manufofinta a ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa nufin mafaka mafita ce ga dukan matsaloli - har ma da manyan matsalolin da mutane ke fuskanta a kowace rana a faɗin duniya ba.
An yi ta kokarin ceto mutane da yawa amma an samu mutuwar mutane biyu.
Amma, a lokacin da aka kai hari, an yi wa mutanen da suka tsira hari.
"Wannan abin damuwa ne", in ji Risa Kusuma, mai shekara 35, a wani wurin kiwon lafiya a garin Palu, don ta kwantar wa ɗanta da ke fama da zazzabi rai.
An samu gawarwakin mutane a cikin motar daukar marasa lafiya a kowane minti.
Babu ruwan sha mai tsafta.
A cikin binciken da aka yi na ceto duk abin da aka samu, an ga mazauna sun koma gidajen da aka lalata.
Daruruwan mutane sun ji rauni kuma asibitoci da girgizar kasa ta 7.5 ta shafa suna cunkoso.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda suka ji rauni, ciki har da Dewey Harris, wanda ya karye kashin baya da kafadu, an ajiye su a waje da Asibitin Sojojin Palo, inda ake kula da su a karkashin sama saboda girgizar da ta biyo baya.
Ya yi kuka game da yadda girgizar kasa ta girgiza lokacin da yake zaune a dakin otal mai hawa biyar tare da matarsa da 'yarsa.
Ba mu da lokacin ceton kanmu.
Na kasance a cikin bango da ya rushe, ina tsammanin", in ji Harris ga manema labarai, "sun zo garin ne don bikin aure.
Na ji muryar matata tana kuka don taimako, sannan kuma babu magana.
Ban san abin da ya faru da ita ko 'ya'yana ba.
Ina fatan suna cikin koshin lafiya.
Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin "ta'addanci" ta hanyar talla
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani shafi hudu a jaridar Amurka ta yau da kullum, inda ta yi nuni da fa'idodin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, an zargi jakadan Amurka a China da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yin yakin neman zabe a kan Beijing.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi tsokaci a ranar Laraba kan takardar da aka biya ta babban jaridar kasar Sin ta Des Moines Register, inda ya zargi kasar Sin da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, wanda kasar Sin ta musanta.
Trump ya zargi Beijing da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, a wani abu da jami'an Amurka suka bayyana wa Reuters a matsayin wani sabon yunkuri na Washington na matsa lamba kan China.
A halin yanzu, Beijing da Washington suna cikin yakin kasuwanci, wanda ya haifar da ƙarin haraji kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da juna.
Masana harkokin kasuwanci na kasar Sin da Amurka sun ce, a farkon wannan yakin cinikayya, an tsara harajin da kasar Sin ta yi na ramuwar gayya don cutar da masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa mai dogon lokaci, wanda babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona ne a kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa.
