Branstad ya rubuta cewa, "Gwamnatin China tana amfani da tarihin Amurka na 'yancin faɗar albarkacin baki da kuma 'yan jarida masu zaman kansu don yada wannan farfaganda ta hanyar tallata tallan da aka biya a cikin rajistar Des Mines".
