Jaridar Die Zeit ta ambato wani kakakin soja, ta ce an dakatar da kaddamar da jirgi na farko na wannan sabon jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg "Rhineland-Pfalz" har zuwa farkon rabin 2019.
An shirya jirgin zai shiga cikin rundunar sojan ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma an sami matsala a cikin wannan babban shiri saboda matsalolin bayan bayarwa.
Jiragen ruwa hudu na Baden-Württemberg da rundunar sojin ruwa ta umarci a 2007 zasu maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An ba da rahoton cewa za su sami makamai masu linzami masu ƙarfi, makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da jiragen ruwa, da wasu fasahohin ɓoye, kamar rage radar, infrared da siginar sauti.
Sauran mahimman fasalulluka sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa - zai yiwu a tura sabbin frigates don matsakaicin shekaru biyu daga tashar jirgin ruwan ƙasar.
Duk da haka, ci gaba da jinkiri yana nufin cewa manyan jiragen ruwa na zamani - waɗanda ya kamata su taimaka wa Jamus ta nuna ƙarfinta a ƙasashen waje - za su zama tsofaffi a lokacin da suka sauka, Die Zeit ta ruwaito.
A shekarar da ta gabata ne aka samu labarin wannan mummunar jirgi mai saukar ungulu mai lamba F125 lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta ki amincewa da shi a hukumance, ta mayar da shi zuwa mashigin jirgin ruwa na Blum & Voss da ke Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojan ruwa ta dawo da jirgi zuwa ga maginin jirgi bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san komai game da dalilan da ke bayan komawar ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu manyan "kurakurai na software da kayan aiki" waɗanda za su sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani a yaƙi.
Abubuwan da ke cikin software suna da mahimmanci, saboda jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg za su kasance da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120 - kusan rabin ma'aikatan tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Bugu da kari, an ga cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai wanda zai rage aikinsa kuma ya hana shi kara haɓaka makomar jirgin.
An yi imanin cewa jirgin mai nauyin tan 7,000 na Rhineland-Palatinate ya ninka nauyin jirgi iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da shi a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Baya ga kayan aiki mara kyau, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya, gami da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin, ya zama matsala.
Daga farkon matakin £ 2.2 biliyan zuwa £ 3.1 biliyan ($ 3.6 biliyan) a cikin mamaki.
Sabbin frigates masu matsala sun zama mafi mahimmanci a cikin sabon gargaɗin da ake yi game da raguwar sojojin ruwa na Jamus.
A farkon wannan shekarar shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus Hans-Peter Bartels ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa na "ta hanyar da ba su da isasshen jirgin ruwa".
