Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami a garin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, jami'ai sun ce adadin wadanda suka mutu na iya karuwa.
A sakamakon katsewar sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su samu labarin komai ba a yankin Donggala Regency da ke arewacin Palau, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
Daga Palu, an ceto mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Dongola a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Babban birnin jihar Tsakiyar Sulawesi shine Palu, wanda ke ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙaramin ƙauye a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ke da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka afkawa.
Dongola wani yanki ne da ke nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Wannan yanki wanda ke da matsayi mafi ƙasƙanci fiye da na jihar yana da kimanin mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Babban tushen tattalin arzikin jihar Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin bakin teku na Dongola, shine kamun kifi da noma.
Har ila yau, ma'adinan nickel suna da mahimmanci a jihar, amma yawancin su suna kusa da bakin tekun Sulawesi, a Morowali.
Hukumar kula da bala'o'i ta Indonesia ta ce, an yi wa Palu da Donggala tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekarar 1938 tsunami ya kashe kusan mutane 200 a Donggala kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje.
Tsunami ya sake afkawa Dongla a shekarar 1996 inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific mai yawan girgizar kasa kuma ana yawan samun girgizar kasa.
Wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru kwanan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar kasa ta haifar da tsunami a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh a Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra wanda ya shafi kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a yankunan bakin tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane daruruwa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, wanda hakan ya haifar da tsunami da ya afku a gabar kudu kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afku a daya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya rutsa da garuruwa da dama kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa mai zurfi ta afkawa yankin Aceh PD Jaya, ta haifar da bala'i da firgici tare da tunatar da mutane game da mummunan tsunami na 2004.
Ko da yake babu wata tsunami da ta faru, amma gidaje sun rushe kuma mutane sama da 100 sun mutu.
2018: Wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Lombo na kasar Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, da yawa a arewacin tsibirin.
